item.title: About me
item.description: My name is Pritish Patil. I am a 2nd year neuroscience masters student at Weizmann Institute of Science, Israel. I am working on working memory the labs of Misha Tsodyks and Ofer Yizhar. “saske je cmaci” is Lojban for science and math which are my major obsessions. Other obsessions include comics (like xkcd), music (like Taylor Swift), linux (like, umm … linux) and reading … lots of reading. 👨‍🔬 studying 🐭🧠 using ⚡,💡🧬, 📹.
